          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mt-1 mr-3 text-accent">‚ñ∏</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary">Open Source Development</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mt-1 mr-3 text-accent">‚ñ∏</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary">Career Development in Tech</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          Please reach out via email with details about your event, and I'll get
          back to you promptly.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
